headline: Strength Seen in Stora Enso Oyj (SEOAY): Can Its 11.3% Jump Turn into More Strength?
summary: Stora Enso Oyj (SEOAY) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.
